title: Ep. 67: The Conference Championships
description:
The Ringer's Robert Mays and Danny Kelly thoroughly break down this Sunday's conference championship games, featuring the Atlanta Falcons hosting the Green Bay Packers (02:05) and the Pittsburgh Steelers traveling to take on the New England Patriots (23:04).
